(86, 1, '2016-02-25 23:42:27', '2016-02-25 23:42:27', '<p style="text-align: center;">Boasting some of the <span class="surline">best talent</span> in Washington, D.C., its no surprise our parties leave the everlasting impression that they do. The music and ambiance play a big role in determining how well the party does, in particular when the right music is played at the right time. That is why the artists we feature in our roster have been carefully hand-picked. Meet our talent...</p>', 'Talent', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-25 23:42:27', '2016-02-25 23:42:27', '', 13, 'http://localhost/skylite-wp/uncategorized/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(87, 1, '2016-02-25 23:49:43', '2016-02-25 23:49:43', '“Music expresses that which cannot be said and on which it is impossible to be silent.” – Victor Hugo\r\n\r\nIt is this fundamental belief of music that Danny House practices. Placing very huge emphasis on quality, original productions, as well as the essence of the live performance, along with a keen sixth sense of being able to read, or feel rather, the wavelengths of those around him. It is a mixture of these elements that build Danny’s musical structure, or system. Danny’s official DJ career began in early 2009. Danny is now a Producer/DJ staple not only in Washington D.C but also in some of the most dynamic cities in the world. With annual appearances at the Winter Music Conference in Miami, and a new presence at the Denver Winter Showcase this March.\r\n\r\nDanny has come a long way since his is start in 2009, his accomplishments in 2014 and 2015 alone are indicative of a bright future for this Producer/DJ and D.C. native. These include performances with international superstars like Stonebridge, Sydney Blu, Stan Kolev, Zenbi, Marco Bailey, Serge Devant, Zenbi, Marc &amp; Kone, Florian Meindl, DJ YSL, DJ Keza (Dubai), Jason Smith, and Kama (Italy); in places that include Paris, Oslo, Stockholm, Miami, and Richmond to name a few.\r\n\r\n[soundcloud]https://soundcloud.com/dannyhouseofficial/[/soundcloud]', 'DANNY HOUSE', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'danny-house', '', '', '2016-02-25 23:51:51', '2016-02-25 23:51:51', '', 0, 'http://localhost/skylite-wp/?p=87', 0, 'post', '', 0),
