(95, 1, '2016-02-26 00:04:31', '2016-02-26 00:04:31', 'A.P. Andres was born in Ecuador and arrived to the States as a young adult, he brought with him his Latin flavor and fussioned with Top 40 Electro/Dance to make a great mix of music that plays every weekend at a SkilyteDC event. His mixes are very diverse and flexible, the smooth transition from genres to genres makes his job an outstanding party experience. He has been part of an Extensive list of clubs in Washington DC, and also plays at private events around the area from Weddings to Corporate events. He started Djing on the year 2000 and has been part of SkyliteDC for almost 5 years..', 'A.P ANDRES', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'a-p-andres', '', '', '2016-02-26 00:05:13', '2016-02-26 00:05:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/skylite-wp/?p=95', 0, 'post', '', 0),
