(109, 1, '2016-02-26 00:10:08', '2016-02-26 00:10:08', '', 'bebe', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'bebe', '', '', '2016-02-26 00:10:08', '2016-02-26 00:10:08', '', 107, 'http://localhost/skylite-wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/bebe.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(110, 1, '2016-02-26 00:11:34', '2016-02-26 00:11:34', 'Cuban started Djing in 2004 while attending High School. His passion for the trade has allowed him to maintain a continuous residency at nightclubs for several years. Two years ago Cuban joined Skylite DC. The concept of being able to play a wide range of genres for a diverse crowd was very appealing to him. Skylite DC gave him the opportunity to expand his music selections beyond the top 40 U.S. tracks being played at most clubs in DC.\r\nCuban has successfully bridge the gap from clubs and private events such as weddings. Cuban performs at over 70 private events every year(40 of them being weddings). The private events have allowed him to understand the history of music from the past several decades. In turn he is able to please crowds of all ages.', 'CUBAN', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cuban', '', '', '2016-02-26 00:11:34', '2016-02-26 00:11:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/skylite-wp/?p=110', 0, 'post', '', 0),
