(129, 1, '2016-02-26 00:20:26', '2016-02-26 00:20:26', 'Randy White has been playing nightclubs and super lounges for over 2 decades. In 1993 Randy was selected to be a Billboard Magazine club reporter. Randy has multiple remixes and songs he has produced for the dance and top 40 market. In 2010 he achieved the milestone of having played for over 1 million people.\r\n\r\nRandy has had the privilege of playing with some of the top djs in the world including Tiesto, Armin Van Buuren, George Acosta, Ferry Corsten, Ralphi Rosario, Victor Calderone to name a few.', 'RANDY WHITE', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'randy-white', '', '', '2016-02-26 00:20:26', '2016-02-26 00:20:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/skylite-wp/?p=129', 0, 'post', '', 0),
