(131, 1, '2016-02-26 00:20:26', '2016-02-26 00:20:26', 'Randy White has been playing nightclubs and super lounges for over 2 decades. In 1993 Randy was selected to be a Billboard Magazine club reporter. Randy has multiple remixes and songs he has produced for the dance and top 40 market. In 2010 he achieved the milestone of having played for over 1 million people.\r\n\r\nRandy has had the privilege of playing with some of the top djs in the world including Tiesto, Armin Van Buuren, George Acosta, Ferry Corsten, Ralphi Rosario, Victor Calderone to name a few.', 'RANDY WHITE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '129-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-26 00:20:26', '2016-02-26 00:20:26', '', 129, 'http://localhost/skylite-wp/uncategorized/129-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(132, 1, '2016-02-26 00:21:25', '2016-02-26 00:21:25', 'Andrey Bazza, originally from Belarus, has been a DJ in Washington DC area for over 10 years.\r\n\r\nAndrey is the owner of Troika Party, a European club portal in DC and co-founder of Euro Junkies. When it comes to European club events, Andrey has been at the forefront both organizing and DJing and Bazza became a household name when it comes to Euro parties in the DC area.\r\n\r\nAndrey Bazza had residency and DJed at some of the best clubs in DC, including Capitale, Cities, District, Eden, Fur, Gazuza, Ibiza, Josephine, Lima, Masa 14, Muse, Opera, Ozio, The Park, Sax, Slaviya, Toro Toro, and Ultrabar. He also shared the stage with some of the biggest names in the EDM industry including Bobina, BT, D:Fuse, Darude, DJ Grad, DJ Korean, Doc Martin, Donald Glaude, Enur, Global Deejays, Jonathan Peters, Junkie XL, Oliver Moldan, Oscar G, Stan Kolev, Starkillers, Stonebridge and Yves Larock. Andrey’s unique style ranges from vocal and commercial Deep House to energy packed Progressive / Electro club sets!', 'ANDREY BAZZA', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'andrey-bazza', '', '', '2016-02-26 00:21:25', '2016-02-26 00:21:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost/skylite-wp/?p=132', 0, 'post', '', 0),
