(135, 1, '2016-02-26 00:29:24', '2016-02-26 00:29:24', '<p style="text-align: left;">Boasting some of the <span class="surline">best talent</span> in Washington, D.C., its no surprise our parties leave the everlasting impression that they do. The music and ambiance play a big role in determining how well the party does, in particular when the right music is played at the right time. That is why the artists we feature in our roster have been carefully hand-picked. Meet our talent...</p>', 'Talent', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-26 00:29:24', '2016-02-26 00:29:24', '', 13, 'http://localhost/skylite-wp/uncategorized/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
